					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That's not right. This is what you need:
<br />
<br />.rsset $300
<br />ControllerButtons: .rs 1
<br />
<br />LDX #$01
<br />STA $4016
<br />DEX
<br />STX $4016
<br />LDX #$08
<br />Loop:
<br />LDA $4016
<br />LSR A 
<br />ROL ControllerButtons
<br />DEX
<br />BNE Loop
<br />RTS ;Controller value in the variable ControllerButtons.
<br />
<br />Maybe look into more 6502. Seems you don't have a good enough understanding of it or the hardware.</div>

